## Task Tracking

This machine uses **beads** (`bd`) for task tracking. Tasks live in `~/.beads/` (git-tracked, will merge with yadm later).

```bash
bd ready              # What can I work on now?
bd show <id>          # Full details on an issue
bd update <id> --status=in_progress  # Start work
bd close <id>         # Complete work
bd list               # All open issues
bd prime              # Full workflow context
```

**Current Epics:**
- `claude-wp-ffo` - MF Kadence-Child Theme (P1) - Spotlightr migration, pressing prod work
- `claude-wp-pj7` - MF Brand Plugin Phase 1 (P2) - Theme parity, on hold
- `claude-wp-a8y` - Bio Theme Speed Improvements (P2) - On hold, biocon icons issue
- `claude-wp-a79` - yadm Dotfiles Setup (P3) - Waiting on home laptop

Run `bd ready` at session start to see available work.

