## Dotfiles Management

Using **yadm** to manage dotfiles across home and work laptops.

- Repository: `https://github.com/fraserYT/dotfiles`
- This machine's class: `work`
- Home laptop class: `home`
- Machine-specific files use `##class.work` / `##class.home` suffix

Status tracked in beads: `claude-wp-a79`

